OL,3,CIncrease in people registered with
OL,4,Cprediabetes in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FThere has been an 11.4% increase in
OL,7,Fthe number of people registered with
OL,8,Fprediabetes in Northern Ireland.
OL,10,FDiabetes UK described the condition as
OL,11,Fwhere a person's blood sugars are
OL,12,Fhigher than usual, but not high enough
OL,13,Ffor them to receive a diagnosis of
OL,14,Ftype 2 diabetes.
