OL,3,CIncrease in people registered with
OL,4,Cprediabetes in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FThe charity said the latest figures
OL,7,Ffrom the department of health also
OL,8,Fhighlights an increase in the number
OL,9,Fof people registered with diabetes
OL,10,Facross the five health care trusts
OL,11,Ffrom just under 112,000 to almost
OL,12,F115,000 over the last 12 months.
OL,14,FDiabetes UK Northern Ireland Interim
OL,15,FNational Director, Roxanne Small,
OL,16,Fdescribed the increase in prediabetes
OL,17,Fas considerable.
