OL,3,CIncrease in people registered with
OL,4,Cprediabetes in Northern Ireland
OL,6,F"These new figures are significant in
OL,7,Fshowing us that nearly 200,000 people
OL,8,Fare living with, or at risk of
OL,9,Fdiabetes in Northern Ireland," she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"In our work, we see first-hand how it
OL,13,Fis an incredibly tough and relentless
OL,14,Fcondition that can have a huge impact
OL,15,Fon a person's life ` therefore, it is
OL,16,Fvitally important that people are
OL,17,Faware of the resources and support
OL,18,Favailable to help manage their health
OL,19,Fand wellbeing.
