OL,3,CIncrease in people registered with
OL,4,Cprediabetes in Northern Ireland
OL,6,F"Whilst the reporting of prediabetes
OL,7,Fcases is relatively new for Northern
OL,8,FIreland, the increase we've seen over
OL,9,Fthe last year is considerable.
OL,11,F"We strongly believe that greater
OL,12,Fawareness and reporting across the
OL,13,Fregion have played a strong role in
OL,14,Fthis rise.
OL,16,F"Prediabetes has been a real topic of
OL,17,Fconversation when speaking with
OL,18,Fmembers of the public as they are keen
OL,19,Fto understand more about it and how
OL,20,Fthey may be able to reduce their risk
OL,21,Fof developing type 2 diabetes."
