OL,4,Cprediabetes in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FShe added: "We understand that for
OL,7,Fsome people it may feel that a
OL,8,Fprediabetes diagnosis means that type
OL,9,F2 diabetes is certain, however, this
OL,10,Fis not always the case.
OL,12,F"While you may be at a higher risk of
OL,13,Fdeveloping type 2 diabetes, many
OL,14,Fpeople can reduce their risk, and it
OL,15,Fmay be possible to prevent or delay
OL,16,Fthe condition from developing.
OL,18,F"For anyone with concerns, we really
OL,19,Fencourage you to contact your
OL,20,Fhealthcare team and reach out to our
OL,21,Fteam for local support.
